# 🩺 MediChat Assist

**MediChat Assist** is a modern web application that provides medical chat assistance through a clean, responsive UI. Built with **React (or Next.js)**, styled using **Tailwind CSS**, and deployed via **Firebase Hosting**, this app combines real-time interaction with elegant design.

## 🔗 Live Demo

👉 [Visit Live App](https://studio--medichat-assist-uvxuj.us-central1.hosted.app)

---

## 🚀 Features

- 💬 Medical chat or bot assistance
- 🌙 Light and dark mode via Tailwind's `darkMode: 'class'`
- 🎨 Theming support using CSS variables (HSL)
- 🎞️ Smooth animations (accordion, message fade-in)
- ⚡ Fast and secure hosting with Firebase
- 📱 Responsive across all devices

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer       | Technology                      |
|-------------|----------------------------------|
| Frontend    | React / Next.js (choose yours)   |
| Styling     | Tailwind CSS (`tailwind.config.ts`) |
| Animations  | `tailwindcss-animate` plugin     |
| Hosting     | Firebase Hosting                 |

---

## 🧩 Tailwind Configuration Highlights

Your `tailwind.config.ts` includes:

- **Dark Mode** support (`darkMode: 'class'`)
- **CSS variable-based theming** for consistent design
- **Custom color tokens** for:
  - `primary`, `secondary`, `accent`, `muted`
  - `sidebar`, `popover`, `card`, `chart`, etc.
- **Animations**:
  - `accordion-down`
  - `accordion-up`
  - `message-in`

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```bash
medichat-assist/
├── public/                 # Static files
├── src/
│   ├── app/                # App routing and layout (Next.js)
│   ├── components/         # Reusable UI components
│   └── pages/              # Page-level components (React or Next.js)
├── tailwind.config.ts      # Tailwind configuration
├── firebase.json           # Firebase hosting config
├── package.json            # Project metadata and scripts
└── README.md               # You're reading this!
